Overview for 2048+

names ("2048...")
	super
	battle
	blast
	arena
	royale
	ultimate
	mint

Move tiles to add and create the 2049 tile.

Get powers from 
	- Creating 2049 tiles
	- Making high scoring moves
	- Doubling highest tile

Powers
	Transmute
		turn a 2 into a 4
	Bomb
		halves a tiles number
	Freeze
		Prevent a tile from merging

Currency is the player's score